name: Slot ter Hoge
author: Annaliese Dempsey
body:
Beschrijving

Name: Slot ter Hoge or 't Slot ter Hooghe

Built: 1726, at a VOC wharf in Middelburg

Chamber: Zeeland

Length: 145 ft

Weight: 425 last, 850 ton

Complement: 180
